{{Quote|The IT-O's greatest tool is reputation. ''Tell'' the suspect you have one, and ''show'' it waiting in the wings. This alone will often elicit a confession.|An excerpt from [[The New Essential Guide to Droids]]|<ref name="The New Essential Guide to Droids">''[[The New Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>}}
'''''Stratagems of the Inquisitorius''''' was a book on the interrogation techniques used by the [[Inquisitorius/Legends|Inquisitorius]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. [[Grand Inquisitor/Legends|Grand Inquisitor]] [[Laddinare Torbin]] wrote it prior to his [[Death/Legends|death]]. It included information about [[IT-O interrogation droid/Legends|IT-O Interrogators]].

